item.title: Wilderness Lodge Resort Logo
item.dc:creator: Brian Kirsten
item.content:encoded: The Wilderness Lodge is architecturally similar to the lodge at Yellowstone National Park. The Wilderness Lodge logo mimics the National Park Service’s basic shape. These similarities help give you a good mind picture of what the overall resort experience will be. I enjoy the way nature is depicted in this logo and it definitely has Yellowstone inspiration.
